OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778217992
OL,3,C'Largest single order' of Airbus
OL,4,Cplanes secures Belfast jobs
OL,6,FOne of Northern Ireland's largest
OL,7,Fmanufacturers has signed a multi-
OL,8,Fbillion-dollar deal which will secure
OL,9,Fjobs in Belfast.
OL,11,FAir Asia has bought 150 A220 jets from
OL,12,FAirbus representing the largest single
OL,13,Forder for such a plane.
OL,15,FThe order brings the total number of
OL,16,Forders for that model to over one
OL,17,Fthousand.
OL,19,FAir Asia said that the 'list price' of
OL,20,Fthe deal is estimated to be worth $19
OL,21,Fbillion dollars.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
