PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778217992
OL,3,C'Largest single order' of Airbus
OL,4,Cplanes secures Belfast jobs
OL,6,FThe A220 has had a long history as it
OL,7,Fstarted life out as the c-series under
OL,8,FBombardier before Airbus took over.
OL,10,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,11,FWednesday, Lars Wagner from Airbus
OL,12,Fsaid: "The 220 is a dream for low-cost
OL,13,Fcarriers.
OL,15,F"It's quiet, it's efficient, and it's
OL,16,Fdesigned for faster boarding, for
OL,17,Flonger routes, and less time in
OL,18,Fhangars. So it doesn't just fly`it
OL,19,Freally performs."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
