PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778217992
OL,3,C'Largest single order' of Airbus
OL,4,Cplanes secures Belfast jobs
OL,6,F1500 people employed at the Belfast
OL,7,Fbase work on manufacturing the
OL,9,FThey manufacture the wings and mid
OL,10,Ffuselage and ship them to an assembly
OL,11,Ffacility in Canada.
OL,13,FThe Canadian Prime Minister welcomed
OL,14,Fthe deal.
OL,16,FMark Carney said: "The A220-300 is a
OL,17,Fshowcase of Canadian ingenuity: lower
OL,18,Ffuel consumption, reduced emissions,
OL,19,Fsmaller noise footprint, advanced
OL,20,Fpropulsion system, lightweight
OL,21,Fmaterials, cutting-edge aerodynamics."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
