OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778217992
OL,3,C'Largest single order' of Airbus
OL,4,Cplanes secures Belfast jobs
OL,6,FThe version being manufactured for Air
OL,7,FAsia will have a new configuration
OL,8,Fwith 10 additional seats.
OL,10,FThere is speculation Airbus could soon
OL,11,Fannounce an even larger version, with
OL,12,Fcapacity for another 40 more
OL,13,Fpassengers.JAir Asia has expressed
OL,14,Finterest in that stretched version.
OL,16,FThe company said they could order
OL,17,Fanother 150 aircraft if they became
OL,18,Favailable.
